~
!item [handle]
Workstation identifier

!item [index]
Colour table index

!end_xlist


!item [(!nolink [Return]) value:]
The function returns the pixel value.

!item [Availability:]
As of NVDI 5.00.

!item [Group:]
Colour table functions

!item [See also:]
(!link [Binding] [Bindings for v_ctab_idx2value])

(!ende_liste)
!end_node



